accessibility.text: My research points after understanding the scope
Venders, Finance people, Invoice processing people
Some venders sending same invoice multiple ways
If there is options for venders to create invoices easily
System should provide a template of invoice where company can accept
Processing manager should receive a notification about new invoices, \u2028Invoice status
Time to reduce for processing a invoice
Vender should know about invoices payment states
Need to have 360 Degree view of invoice for every user

A company is getting invoice from multiple locations, in multiple ways with multiple formats. Company wants to have centralised location, where user can submit invoices in easy manner by avoiding the different invoice formats. Also making sure the invoice processing is very smooth
